	<title2><![CDATA[Meeting with Dr. Cardonza – Collecting Information and Determining Next Steps]]></title2>
	<instructions><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:bold; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">Which question will you ask Dr. Cardonza next?</welcomeText>]]></instructions>
	<choices>
